    "Specifically, our framework can handle a generic multi-turn MDP in the LLM setting, as long as states and actions are defined as sequences of tokens.",
    "The transition kernel in particular can be more general compared to (2), which encodes SR-specific logic.",
    "Indeed, our approach is applicable in many related multi-turn applications (usually involving at least one other human agent), such as general user-facing chatbots (Han et al., 2025), AI travel agents (Hong et al., 2023), customer service chatbots (Brynjolfsson et al., 2025; Ni et al., 2024), and educational tutoring agents (Shani et al., 2024; Nam et al., 2025).",
